                <head>No. 51<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On September 10, Secretary <persName corresp="#p_ADG1">Acheson</persName> made a
                    statement at a press conference denouncing the treatment of Americans imprisoned
                    in Communist China and specifically discussing four cases of Americans who had
                    died in prison or shortly after their release; the text of his statement is
                    printed in Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, September 22,
                    1952, page 440.</p>
            </div>
